Rating: 4
This is the best carrot recipe I've ever tasted. I made it for a dinner party and it was the most popular dish of the evening. The carrots are light and wonderfully flavorable, and were so simple to make! I steamed a bag of fresh baby carrots in the microwave before my guests arrived. When dinner time rolled around, I melted a little butter in a frying pan, tossed in the carrots, and squeezed about 1/2 a lemon on top. I topped it with a couple sprigs of chopped fresh rosemary, stirred, and wow!!!!! Fragrant and fresh and delicious. I already received requests for the recipe. I will make this again and again. It really is the best.

