I served this with Christmas dinner to rave reviews and requests for the recipe. It was fast and easy to make but didn't taste like it. I cooked the carrots tender rather than tender crisp. The carrots probably could be cooked and the sauce made in the morning or even the night before and then combined and reheated just before serving to save time when preparing a company dinner.

